body:
Comment 4: 
Thanks.  The problem is pretty clearly this line:

0x0000000000000001 (NEEDED)             Shared library: []

How did that get there?  It implies that 6l decided to add a library with no name. 
There was a change a couple of months ago to permit #pragma dynimport SYM SYM "" in
which the library has no name; is there any chance that you are somehow using a 6l which
precedes that change?  Check every 6l on your PATH.
